Package: montyhall
Title: Monty Hall Strategy Simulator
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Leal", , "drleal@asu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package breaks down the Monty Hall problem into separate parts to examine how the game functions and how the contestant strategy affects gameplay and ultimately results; additionally, this package uses the Monty Hall data set to run simulations to ensure each function operates as expected.
Depends:
    dplyr
